ComicInfo.Summary:
Just as the girls are targeted by the Friendly Neighborhood Organized Crime Group, Kai and Noemi are confronted with the drama of romance and jealousy -- because love doesn't just hit pause when bigger things are happening. Filled with the dynamic and dramatic action scenes you've come to expect from artist Fabian Lelay and the femme punk palettes of Mara Carpenter.
Note: The digital edition (12/21/2016) for this issue was released before the print edition.
